OL,7,FCompensation for customers receiving
OL,8,Fpoor services from water companies who
OL,9,Fare failing to meet standards could
OL,10,Fmore than double under new Government
OL,11,Fproposals.
OL,13,FAs part of the plans, the list of
OL,14,Fcircumstances that can trigger
OL,15,Fcompensation will also be expanded,
OL,16,Fincluding automatic payments for those
OL,17,Fissued boil notices or when water
OL,18,Fcompanies fail to conduct meter
OL,19,Freadings or installations as promised.
