OL,7,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said
OL,8,Fthe Government hopes to "turn the tide
OL,9,Fon the destruction of our waterways".
OL,11,FThe proposals, which will be subject
OL,12,Fto an eight-week consultation, will
OL,13,Fincrease the amount of reimbursement
OL,14,Fthat customers are legally entitled to
OL,15,Fwhen standards are not met by water
OL,16,Fcompanies.
