OL,7,FFor households impacted by an
OL,8,Fincorrect notice of planned supply
OL,9,Finterruption, compensation will rise
OL,10,Ffrom #20 to #50, meanwhile
OL,11,Freimbursement for internal flooding
OL,12,Ffrom sewers will increase from a
OL,13,Fmaximum of #1,000 to #2,000.
OL,15,FEarlier this year, around 16,000
OL,16,Fresidents of Brixham, Devon, were left
OL,17,Fwithout tap water for eight weeks, and
OL,18,Fwere told to boil their water before
OL,19,Fdrinking it, cooking with it, or
OL,20,Fbrushing their teeth.
