OL,7,FIf the compensation changes had been
OL,8,Fin place when the outages occurred,
OL,9,Fthe residents would have automatically
OL,10,Fbeen entitled to payments. But the
OL,11,FGovernment has said the regulations
OL,12,Fwill not apply retrospectively.
OL,14,FAnnouncing the proposals, Mr Reed
OL,15,Fsaid: "Our water industry is broken.
OL,16,FAfter years of failure, households and
OL,17,Fbusinesses have been let down by water
OL,18,Fcompanies time and time again.
