OL,7,FJenny Suggate, director of policy,
OL,8,Fresearch and campaigns at CCW, said:
OL,9,F"We're delighted the Government is
OL,10,Ffast-tracking efforts to improve the
OL,11,FGuaranteed Standards Scheme, with the
OL,12,Fpotential to boost compensation and
OL,13,Fsupport for hundreds of thousands of
OL,14,Fpeople each year when they are let
OL,15,Fdown by their water company.
