OL,7,F"Given that there has been little
OL,8,Fchange to the standards since they
OL,9,Fwere first introduced, an overhaul is
OL,10,Flong overdue, and we know it is a
OL,11,Fpressing priority for household and
OL,12,Fbusiness customers.
OL,14,F"Demanding higher standards of service
OL,15,Fand improving levels of compensation
OL,16,Fwhen things go wrong will incentivise
OL,17,Fwater companies to get things right
OL,18,Fthe first time for all customers."
