OL,7,FThe Guaranteed Standards Scheme, which
OL,8,Fcovers timely restoration of water
OL,9,Fsupply following an interruption,
OL,10,Fresponding to written complaints, and
OL,11,Fmanaging the risk of sewer flooding,
OL,12,Fis being updated for the first time
OL,13,Fsince 2000.
OL,15,FThis comes as water companies face
OL,16,Fcriticism for their handling of
OL,17,Fsewage, with Ofwat proposing #168
OL,18,Fmillion of fines for three of
OL,19,FEngland's biggest water companies.
