OL,7,FThe penalties include a #104 million
OL,8,Fpenalty for Thames Water, #47 million
OL,9,Fpenalty for Yorkshire Water and #17
OL,10,Fmillion for Northumbrian Water for
OL,11,Ffailing to manage sewage spills.
OL,13,FThe Government has previously
OL,14,Fannounced a Water (Special Measures)
OL,15,FBill to cut sewage spills and attract
OL,16,Finvestment to upgrade infrastructure.
