OL,7,FLiberal Democrat Environment
OL,8,Fspokesperson Tim Farron MP said of
OL,9,Fplans to boost compensation: "We will
OL,10,Fscrutinise these proposals closely and
OL,11,Fwelcome any attempts to crack down on
OL,12,Fthese greedy firms but make no
OL,13,Fmistake, our water industry needs top
OL,14,Fto bottom reform.
OL,16,F"That must start with abolishing Ofwat
OL,17,Fand replacing it with a new regulator
OL,18,Fwith real teeth to clampdown on these
OL,19,Fpolluting firms, end the sewage
OL,20,Fscandal and get bill payers the fair
OL,21,Fdeal they deserve."
